
"A Fully Functional Calculator" - This application supports basic arithmetic operations, allowing users to perform addition, subtraction, 
multiplication, and division effortlessly.

User-Friendly Interface:Designed with the user in mind, the interface is intuitive and easy to navigate, providing a seamless experience
for performing calculations.

Real Calculator Feel:I've paid special attention to the design to replicate the look and feel of a real calculator. The aesthetic appeal 
enhances the user experience, making it both functional and visually pleasing.

GUI Library: Python Tkinter
Programming concepts: I've implemented modular design using functions. This not only enhances code readability but also facilitates future
modifications and additions.
